@104 /*CHARNAME*/ = ~I'm glad to hear it. I feel much the same.~
@105 /*Mazzy*/ = ~The future will be what it will be. Odds are that we will both die bravely within the year.~
@106 /*CHARNAME*/ = ~Well, I hope we survive longer than that. I have enjoyed my time with you.~
@107 /*CHARNAME*/ = ~Oh good, I feared you were getting emotionally attached.~
